text: The Beimen Island Presbyterian Church () is a church in Beimen District, Tainan, Taiwan. ==History== The church was originally established in September 1959 as part of the Beimen Mission. In May 1960, the church began accepting patients. They distributed free clothing and groceries. ==See also== * Christianity in Taiwan * Taiwan Blackfoot Disease Socio-Medical Service Memorial House ==References== Category:1959 establishments in Taiwan Category:Churches in Tainan Category:Churches completed in 1959
